Ehjazili

The Ehjazili website is an electronic platform dedicated to booking appointments with doctors, where users can search for doctors according to different specialties. Here is a description of the site's features:

F2 .

Features

  • 1. Simple user interface:

  • User-friendly design helps patients search for doctors easily.

  • 2. Advanced search:

  • The ability to search by specialty, geographic location, and ratings.

  • 3. Appointment scheduling:

  • Patients can book appointments directly through the website and choose the time that suits them.

  • 4. Doctors' evaluation:

  • The ability to write ratings and reviews for doctors after the visit, which helps others choose the right doctor.

  • 5. Notifications:

  • Alerts to users to remind them of their upcoming appointments.

  • 6. Comprehensive information:

  • Detailed information about each doctor, including specialty, CV, and accepted insurances.

  • 7. Technical support:

  • Customer service is available to answer patients' inquiries and help them solve any problems.

  • How it works:

  • 1. User registration:

  • Patients must create an account to be able to book appointments.

  • 2. Search for Doctors:

  • Using the search feature, patients can find doctors within their specialties.

  • 3. Book an Appointment:

  • After selecting the doctor and specialty, the available time for the reservation is determined.

  • 4. Confirmation:

  • The user receives a confirmation via email or text message.

  • 5. Doctor Visit:

  • The patient attends the appointment at the specified time.

  • Benefits:

  • It makes it easier for patients to reach doctors and saves time and effort.

  • It contributes to improving the patient experience by providing multiple options and realistic reviews.
